ars\" style=\"display:inline-flex\"><svg width=\"11\" height=\"11\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"#facc15\"><path d=\"M12 2l3 7h7l-5.5 4.5L18 22l-6-4-6 4 1.5-8.5L2 9h7z\"></path></svg></span><span class=\"ts-stars\" style=\"display:inline-flex\"><svg width=\"11\" height=\"11\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"#facc15\"><path d=\"M12 2l3 7h7l-5.5 4.5L18 22l-6-4-6 4 1.5-8.5L2 9h7z\"></path></svg></span><span class=\"ts-stars\" style=\"display:inline-flex\"><svg width=\"11\" height=\"11\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"#facc15\"><path d=\"M12 2l3 7h7l-5.5 4.5L18 22l-6-4-6 4 1.5-8.5L2 9h7z\"></path></svg></span></span><p style=\"margin:0;font-size:12.5px;color:rgba(255,255,255,.55);font-style:italic;line-height:1.6\">“<!-- -->Recomendo totalmente. Excelente capacidade de transformar ideias em processos claros.<!-- -->”</p><span style=\"font-size:11px;color:var(--muted-2);font-weight:600\">— <!-- -->Ricardo Jesus, Proprietário</span></div><div style=\"padding:16px;border-radius:14px;border:1px solid var(--line);background:rgba(255,255,255,.025);display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:8px\"><span style=\"display:flex;gap:3px\"><span class=\"ts-stars\" style=\"display:inline-flex\"><svg width=\"11\" height=\"11\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"#facc15\"><path d=\"M12 2l3 7h7l-5.5 4.5L18 22l-6-4-6 4 1.5-8.5L2 9h7z\"></path></svg></span><span class=\"ts-stars\" style=\"display:inline-flex\"><svg width=\"11\" height=\"11\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"#facc15\"><path d=\"M12 2l3 7h7l-5.5 4.5L18 22l-6-4-6 4 1.5-8.5L2 9h7z\"></path></svg></span><span class=\"ts-stars\" style=\"display:inline-flex\"><svg width=\"11\" height=\"11\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"#facc15\"><path d=\"M12 2l3 7h7l-5.5 4.5L18 22l-6-4-6 4 1.5-8.5L2 9h7z\"></path></svg></span><span class=\"ts-stars\" style=\"display:inline-flex\"><svg width=\"11\" height=\"11\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"#facc15\"><path d=\"M12 2l3 7h7l-5.5 4.5L18 22l-6-4-6 4 1.5-8.5L2 9h7z\"></path></svg></span><span class=\"ts-stars\" style=\"